name: High Five
description:
High Five is a little game I developed in 6 weeks during Pixelles Montreal incubator. I am new to Unity or game development so please be kind.

You have to use the right finger for each level.  
A short press on the space bar for short jump
A long press on the space bar for long jump

Music : "The Ballad Of The Bravest Finger" by Minouche Briot
Game Design, Art & Developpement Charlye Benoit
